1. we will create the two buckets with  different names.
2. we will create the IAM roles  by adding the s3fullacess in it. 
3. After that we will create the lambda function by using the code language python 3.9.
4. In the execution role , we will use the IAM role which we have created earlier.
5. Then we will create the lambda function.
6. After that we will add the trigger and add s3 source bucket  and event type will be 'all object create event'.
7. After thhat we will add the code given code. 
8. hit the deploy button. 
9. after that we will upload the files in the source loaction. 
10. The magic will happen , the files which you have uploaded in the source location, that files is also there in the target location.
